			<h2><a href="http://www.dorkbot.org/dorkbotbristol/?p=67" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to DepicT! opens for audience voting">DepicT! opens for audience voting</a></h2>
			<h4>October 17th, 2007<!-- by Emma --> &middot; <a href="http://www.dorkbot.org/dorkbotbristol/?p=67#respond" title="Comment on DepicT! opens for audience voting">No Comments</a></h4>
			<div class="entry">
				<p>Have your say as to which of the shortlisted <a href="http://www.depict.org" target="_blank" onclick="javascript:urchinTracker('/outbound/www.depict.org?ref=/dorkbotbristol/index.php?paged=4');">DepicT!</a> films should win the <a href="http://shootingpeople.org/account/auth.php" target="_blank" onclick="javascript:urchinTracker('/outbound/shootingpeople.org/account/auth.php?ref=/dorkbotbristol/index.php?paged=4');">Shooting People</a> Audience Award by voting <a href="http://www.depict.org/news/43" target="_blank" onclick="javascript:urchinTracker('/outbound/www.depict.org/news/43?ref=/dorkbotbristol/index.php?paged=4');">online now</a>. DepicT! is the ultra-short film competition (90 seconds or less) and part of forthcoming <a href="http://www.encounters-festival.org.uk/" target="_blank" onclick="javascript:urchinTracker('/outbound/www.encounters-festival.org.uk/?ref=/dorkbotbristol/index.php?paged=4');">Encounters Festival.</a></p>
<p>The Audience Award filmmakers will receive: a copy of &#8216;Get Your Short Film Funded, Made and Seen&#8217;; Shooting People DVD releases Best vs Best Vols.1 &amp; 2 and Two; and a lifetime membership to Shooting People.<br />
Shortlist DepicT! films are also eligible for the DepicT! Award, judged by a panel of figures from all areas of the film industry, including director Royston Tan and Aardman Animations’ David Sproxton.<br />
DepicT! is a <a href="http://www.watershed.co.uk" target="_blank" onclick="javascript:urchinTracker('/outbound/www.watershed.co.uk?ref=/dorkbotbristol/index.php?paged=4');">Watershed</a> project supported by <a href="http://www.aardman.com" target="_blank" onclick="javascript:urchinTracker('/outbound/www.aardman.com?ref=/dorkbotbristol/index.php?paged=4');">Aardman Animations</a>, <a href="http://www.filmsat59.com/" target="_blank" onclick="javascript:urchinTracker('/outbound/www.filmsat59.com/?ref=/dorkbotbristol/index.php?paged=4');">Films@59</a>, <a href="http://www.artsalliancemedia.com/" target="_blank" onclick="javascript:urchinTracker('/outbound/www.artsalliancemedia.com/?ref=/dorkbotbristol/index.php?paged=4');">Arts Alliance Media</a>, <a href="http://www.bbc.co.uk/filmnetwork/" target="_blank" onclick="javascript:urchinTracker('/outbound/www.bbc.co.uk/filmnetwork/?ref=/dorkbotbristol/index.php?paged=4');">BBC Film Network</a> and Shooting People, the winners will be announced alongside the main DepicT! Award at the Encounters Awards Ceremony on Sat 24 Nov.</p>
<br /><div class='pLink'><a href="http://www.addthis.com/bookmark.php" onclick="javascript:urchinTracker('/outbound/www.addthis.com/bookmark.php?ref=/dorkbotbristol/index.php?paged=4'); window.open('http://www.addthis.com/bookmark.php?pub=&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dorkbot.org%2Fdorkbotbristol%2F%3Fp%3D67&amp;title=DepicT%21+opens+for+audience+voting', 'addthis', 'scrollbars=yes,menubar=no,width=620,height=520,resizable=yes,toolbar=no,location=no,status=no'); return false;" title="Bookmark using any bookmark manager!" rel="external"><img src="http://s3.addthis.com/button1-bm.gif" alt="Social Bookmarking Tool"/></a></div>			</div>	
