			<h2><a href="http://www.dorkbot.org/dorkbotbristol/?p=66" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Medical Robots: Touching A Nerve">Medical Robots: Touching A Nerve</a></h2>
			<h4>October 16th, 2007<!-- by Emma --> &middot; <a href="http://www.dorkbot.org/dorkbotbristol/?p=66#respond" title="Comment on Medical Robots: Touching A Nerve">No Comments</a></h4>
			<div class="entry">
				<h2 id="page-title">6th November 2007</h2>
<p id="article-detail-tower">&nbsp;</p>
<p id="article-detail-rectangle">&nbsp;</p>
<p><a href="http://www.imeche.org/index.htm" onclick="javascript:urchinTracker('/outbound/www.imeche.org/index.htm?ref=/dorkbotbristol/index.php?paged=4');">The Institute of Mechanical Engineering</a> will host a lecture by Cybernetics Professor, <a href="http://www.kevinwarwick.com/" onclick="javascript:urchinTracker('/outbound/www.kevinwarwick.com/?ref=/dorkbotbristol/index.php?paged=4');">Kevin Warwick</a> of Reading University, on the 6th November at <a href="http://www.uwe.ac.uk/" onclick="javascript:urchinTracker('/outbound/www.uwe.ac.uk/?ref=/dorkbotbristol/index.php?paged=4');">UWE</a>.</p>
<p>&#8220;Medical Robots, Touching A Nerve&#8221;, will consider the state of play concerning implant technology and its use; both for therapeutic help and human enhancement. The main emphasis will be on neural implants - implants which make a direct connection in the human brain and nervous system. A look will also be taken at where the technology is taking us. We are about to witness a brain within a brain - that is a computer brain controlling certain aspects of the human brain, from within.</p>
<p>Kevin will also report on his own research which has already resulted in extra-sensory input, extending the nervous system over the internet and electronic communication directly between human brains.</p>
<p><a href="http://nearyou.imeche.org.uk/events/event.htm?eID=1208" onclick="javascript:urchinTracker('/outbound/nearyou.imeche.org.uk/events/event.htm?eID=1208?ref=/dorkbotbristol/index.php?paged=4');">More information</a></p>
<br /><div class='pLink'><a href="http://www.addthis.com/bookmark.php" onclick="javascript:urchinTracker('/outbound/www.addthis.com/bookmark.php?ref=/dorkbotbristol/index.php?paged=4'); window.open('http://www.addthis.com/bookmark.php?pub=&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dorkbot.org%2Fdorkbotbristol%2F%3Fp%3D66&amp;title=Medical+Robots%3A+Touching+A+Nerve', 'addthis', 'scrollbars=yes,menubar=no,width=620,height=520,resizable=yes,toolbar=no,location=no,status=no'); return false;" title="Bookmark using any bookmark manager!" rel="external"><img src="http://s3.addthis.com/button1-bm.gif" alt="Social Bookmarking Tool"/></a></div>			</div>	
