			<h2><a href="http://www.dorkbot.org/dorkbotbristol/?p=65" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to October Dorkbot">October Dorkbot</a></h2>
			<h4>October 12th, 2007<!-- by Emma --> &middot; <a href="http://www.dorkbot.org/dorkbotbristol/?p=65#respond" title="Comment on October Dorkbot">No Comments</a></h4>
			<div class="entry">
				<p class="entry">
<p class="snap_preview">Welcome back after the summer break, Dorkbot returns Tuesday 16th October, 7pm at <a href="http://www.watershed.co.uk/" title="Watershed" target="_blank" onclick="javascript:urchinTracker('/outbound/www.watershed.co.uk/?ref=/dorkbotbristol/index.php?paged=4');">Watershed</a>.</p>
<p>The line up looks like this:</p>
<p>1) From waterproof robots to crazy patents; from light sabers in space to designing a new nuclear bomb, 2007 has been yet another crazy year in science and technology. Dr Andrew Impey from <a href="http://www.null-hypothesis.co.uk/" title="Null hyphothesis" target="_blank" onclick="javascript:urchinTracker('/outbound/www.null-hypothesis.co.uk/?ref=/dorkbotbristol/index.php?paged=4');">Null Hypothesis</a>, the online Journal of Unlikely Science will be highlighting some of the more weird and bizarre stories to make the news this year.</p>
<p>And…</p>
<p>2) John Honniball presents “What can you make with microcontrollers?”<br />
Microcontrollers are very popular with gadget builders who need a little more intelligence in their circuits. But what exactly are they and what can you do with them? This demo will show just what’s involved when you want to add a microcontroller to your gadget, and will introduce the creative possibilities of combining electronic hardware with embedded software. So, what could you do with a computer-on-a-chip that’s far smaller, cheaper and less power-hungry than the PC or Mac?</p>
<br /><div class='pLink'><a href="http://www.addthis.com/bookmark.php" onclick="javascript:urchinTracker('/outbound/www.addthis.com/bookmark.php?ref=/dorkbotbristol/index.php?paged=4'); window.open('http://www.addthis.com/bookmark.php?pub=&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dorkbot.org%2Fdorkbotbristol%2F%3Fp%3D65&amp;title=October+Dorkbot', 'addthis', 'scrollbars=yes,menubar=no,width=620,height=520,resizable=yes,toolbar=no,location=no,status=no'); return false;" title="Bookmark using any bookmark manager!" rel="external"><img src="http://s3.addthis.com/button1-bm.gif" alt="Social Bookmarking Tool"/></a></div>			</div>	
