			<h2><a href="http://www.dorkbot.org/dorkbotbristol/?p=63" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Artists Research Residencies in Spain">Artists Research Residencies in Spain</a></h2>
			<h4>September 17th, 2007<!-- by Clare --> &middot; <a href="http://www.dorkbot.org/dorkbotbristol/?p=63#respond" title="Comment on Artists Research Residencies in Spain">No Comments</a></h4>
			<div class="entry">
				<p>Call for artists to work on research projects in 9 companies and investigation centres in Spain<br />
Deadline for applications: 3 October 2007, 9 am.<br />
Collaboration period: November 2007 – July 2008 (9 months, part-time)</p>
<p>DISONANCIAS is pleased to announce the call for proposals from international artists to work on joint research projects with companies and research centres located in the Basque Country (Spain).</p>
<p>DISONANCIAS <http:>  is a platform that promotes relationships between artists and companies, research centres or public organisations in order to foster innovation in all its aspects and transmit to society the importance of developing creative environments. </http:></p>
